{{Infobox quest |name = Vampiric Rush |image = XC3 Challenge Battle Mode.png |description = "Life-draining monsters assemble at Archsage favorite Great Cotte Falls! Archsage sweating with anticipation!" |giver = [[Nopon Archsage]] |location = [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]] |difficultyCB3= 2 |prereqs = Chapter 4 started |rewards = 500-800 [[Noponstone]]s (Normal) }} '''Vampiric Rush''' is a Time Attack [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] in {{XC3}}. It can be received from [[Nopon Archsage]] in the [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]], available as downloadable content from the second part of the Expansion Pass. Clearing this challenge with at least an A rank for the first time will unlock the Swimwear A outfit for [[Lanz]].
